# Local development environment template.
# Copy to `.env.local` and fill in.
#
# IMPORTANT: every variable listed here is exposed by Cloudflare's
# Deploy-with-Cloudflare wizard as an editable form field at install
# time. Keep this file minimal — only put what every user must set.
# Optional integration secrets (Turnstile, Sentry, Stripe, HubSpot,
# GitHub, Discord, VERCEL_REDEPLOY_URL, …) belong in the README's
# "Optional integrations" table and are set post-deploy via
# Dashboard → Worker → Settings → Variables and Secrets.

PAYLOAD_SECRET="openssl rand -hex 32"
